### Contacts API Testing

# Set your base URL (change this to your deployed URL when testing on Render)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Get all contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts

### Get specific contact by ID
# Replace with actual contact ID from your database
